[For a map of Bulgaria, go to http://www.lib.utexas.edu/maps/europe/bulgaria.jpg. Razgrad is in central Ruse, and Shumen is in Varna; both provinces are in NE Bulgaria.

This report indicates that one or more additional cases of bovine anthrax have been reported in north west Bulgaria. Disease problems like company. It appears that the regional Bulgarian veterinary services are badly stretched at present. - Mod.MHJ

A HealthMap/ProMED-mail map can be accessed at: https://promedmail.org/promed-post?place=2748884,81.]
